text: @FedExHelp Why won't you let me add my work address to my profile on your site? Package that WAS going to be delivered while I'm home today now coming while I'm at work tomorrow. Needs to go to work to reach me, not home to sit out & be stolen!! #fedexsucks

@ISanderson Hello, this is LaShelia.  I'd like to check on your options.  Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r

@FedExHelp Only shipper can change delivery address? Dismissive CS staff? Is there ANYTHING you don't excel at being the worst at? I can't even leave an accurate survey response because your 1-5 scale doesn't allow for zero or negative numbers. #fedexsucks
@ISanderson Allow me to check into the shipment in order to see if only your shipper has authorization to do so.  I'm sorry for any inconvenience or frustration that was caused.
